            <td width="100%">
            <div id="customerLogo">&nbsp;</div>
            <div id="messagebody" style="font: 12px verdana">&nbsp;</div>
            <div id="Signature" style="font: 12px verdana">
            <div style="margin: 0in 0in 0pt"><span style="font-family: Candara; font-size: 11pt">Hi, </span></div>
            <div style="margin: 0in 0in 0pt">&nbsp;</div>
            <div style="margin: 0in 0in 0pt"><span style="font-family: Candara; font-size: 11pt">I have an immediate requirement opening for a <strong><span style="background: yellow">.Net Developer position in Ann Arbor, MI. This is a Long-Term Contract position</span></strong>. I would appreciate if you could send your updated word format resume along with best contact details ASAP.</span></div>
            <div style="margin: 0in 0in 0pt">&nbsp;</div>
            <div style="margin: 0in 0in 0pt"><span style="font-family: Candara; font-size: 11pt">Here are the requirement details:</span></div>
            <div style="margin: 0in 0in 0pt">&nbsp;</div>
            <div style="margin: 0in 0in 0pt"><strong><span style="font-family: Candara; color: blue; font-size: 11pt">Position &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; : .Net Developer</span></strong></div>
            <div style="margin: 0in 0in 0pt"><strong><span style="font-family: Candara; color: blue; font-size: 11pt">Location &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; : Ann Arbor, MI</span></strong></div>
            <div style="margin: 0in 0in 0pt"><strong><span style="font-family: Candara; color: blue; font-size: 11pt">Duration &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; : long-Term Contract</span></strong></div>
            <div style="margin: 0in 0in 0pt">&nbsp;</div>
            <div style="margin: 0in 0in 0pt"><span style="font-family: Candara; font-size: 11pt">ASP.NET and C# development; </span></div>
            <div style="margin: 0in 0in 0pt"><span style="font-family: Candara; font-size: 11pt">JQuery; MSVS; Oracle PLSQL </span></div>
            <div style="margin: 0in 0in 0pt">&nbsp;</div>
            <ul type="disc" style="margin-top: 0in">
                <li style="margin: 0in 0in 0pt"><span style="font-family: Candara; font-size: 11pt">Web/Application developer with experience in 3 tier architecture. I am looking for a developer who is familiar with 3 tier ASP.NET/C#/Web Services architecture. This is a business internet banking product that focus on small to medium size businesses. The person needs to be self motivated and able to work with a small team. You will be responsible for all phases of development from technical specifications through code development and unit testing.</span></li>
                <li style="margin: 0in 0in 0pt"><span style="font-family: Candara; font-size: 11pt">Write Quality Source Code - Writes source code to fix identified problems, add new features, or develop a new application utilizing FIS's programming standards and methodologies. Source code is of high quality as demonstrated by the application working properly and there being few errors or few fixes identified by others. Exhibits knowledge of more than one programming language. Writes source code independently. Looks for and ensures coding efficiencies within application(s).</span></li>
                <li style="margin: 0in 0in 0pt"><span style="font-family: Candara; font-size: 11pt">Translate Business Requirements Into Programming Design - Coordinates with business analysts or other internal professionals to clearly understand client needs. Translates these business requirements into programming design and accurately estimates tasks. Based upon knowledge of the application, determines what needs to be changed or enhanced to meet the functional needs. Designs a solution that solves the identified problem. Determines specific actions which must be taken to meet the need. Provides input on the time it will take to do the project and the resources needed.</span></li>
                <li style="margin: 0in 0in 0pt"><span style="font-family: Candara; font-size: 11pt">Suggest New System Alternatives - Can provide new and innovative alternative solutions to system challenges. Is not limited to merely repeating what others have done but can create new, alternative ways to approach things. Is comfortable working in unstructured situations where creativity is needed. Can brainstorm alternatives to a given problem. Will pioneer new ways of doing things that are ultimately used by others.</span></li>
                <li style="margin: 0in 0in 0pt"><span style="font-family: Candara; font-size: 11pt">Complete Project Assignments - The ability to handle multiple medium projects commensurate with job expectations. The ability to handle medium project complexity commensurate with job expectations.</span></li>
                <li style="margin: 0in 0in 0pt"><span style="font-family: Candara; font-size: 11pt">Communicate Effectively - Effective verbal communications. Writing is organized, flows well, has a clear message, and a business perspective.</span></li>
                <li style="margin: 0in 0in 0pt"><span style="font-family: Candara; font-size: 11pt">Solve Problems - Effective problem solving competence for various programming challenges. Can analyze what the problem is and brainstorm a number of possible solutions. Before seeking additional help in solving problem has exhausted all individual means available.</span></li>
                <li style="margin: 0in 0in 0pt"><span style="font-family: Candara; font-size: 11pt">Demonstrate Resourcefulness - Is not content to merely wait for others to provide solutions or suggest alternatives.</span></li>
                <li style="margin: 0in 0in 0pt"><span style="font-family: Candara; font-size: 11pt">Manage Time Effectively - Is aware of project timelines and meets timelines.</span></li>
            </ul>
            <div style="margin: 0in 0in 0pt">&nbsp;</div>
            <div style="margin: 0in 0in 0pt"><span style="font-family: Candara; font-size: 11pt">Knowledge, Skills and Abilities:</span></div>
            <ul type="disc" style="margin-top: 0in">
                <li style="margin: 0in 0in 0pt"><span style="font-family: Candara; font-size: 11pt">Considerable knowledge of Data Networks </span></li>
                <li style="margin: 0in 0in 0pt"><span style="font-family: Candara; font-size: 11pt">Considerable knowledge of Web Security </span></li>
                <li style="margin: 0in 0in 0pt"><span style="font-family: Candara; font-size: 11pt">Considerable knowledge of internet development and debugging tools</span></li>
                <li style="margin: 0in 0in 0pt"><span style="font-family: Candara; font-size: 11pt">Considerable knowledge of web services, technology, and tools</span></li>
                <li style="margin: 0in 0in 0pt"><span style="font-family: Candara; font-size: 11pt">Considerable knowledge of data modeling </span></li>
                <li style="margin: 0in 0in 0pt"><span style="font-family: Candara; font-size: 11pt">Considerable knowledge of graphic &amp; functional design </span></li>
                <li style="margin: 0in 0in 0pt"><span style="font-family: Candara; font-size: 11pt">Considerable knowledge of the differences between how an application works on a local machine versus a server</span></li>
                <li style="margin: 0in 0in 0pt"><span style="font-family: Candara; font-size: 11pt">Considerable knowledge of the differences among various types of browsers and browser versions </span></li>
                <li style="margin: 0in 0in 0pt"><span style="font-family: Candara; font-size: 11pt">Skill in project management </span></li>
                <li style="margin: 0in 0in 0pt"><span style="font-family: Candara; font-size: 11pt">Skill in developing code for the client or the server</span></li>
                <li style="margin: 0in 0in 0pt"><span style="font-family: Candara; font-size: 11pt">Skill in at least one client side scripting language</span></li>
                <li style="margin: 0in 0in 0pt"><span style="font-family: Candara; font-size: 11pt">Ability to identify and correct basic coding errors</span></li>
                <li style="margin: 0in 0in 0pt"><span style="font-family: Candara; font-size: 11pt">Ability to implement a design using the project-specific tools</span></li>
                <li style="margin: 0in 0in 0pt"><span style="font-family: Candara; font-size: 11pt">Ability to manage and coordinate test activities for assigned application</span></li>
                <li style="margin: 0in 0in 0pt"><span style="font-family: Candara; font-size: 11pt">Ability to communicate effectively verbally and in writing</span></li>
                <li style="margin: 0in 0in 0pt"><span style="font-family: Candara; font-size: 11pt">Ability to establish and maintain effective working relationships with employees, clients and public</span></li>
            </ul>
            <div style="margin: 0in 0in 0pt">&nbsp;</div>
